overview.en: ZBT is dedicated to build a value discovery platform for game assets exchanging platform, and build a digital blockchain game assets leading the world.ZBT community users can trade game assets at www.zbt.com. Gamers with Zabit (ZBT) points can get more service content on the platform.
overview.zh: 扎比特(ZBT)致力于打造专业的游戏资产交易市场。致力于打造全球领先的区块链游戏资产交易社区，扎比特社区用户可以在WWW.ZBT.COM进行游戏资产交易，拥有扎比特(ZBT)积分的用户可以得到平台更多服务内容。
